{"tid":2195695,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴郡榮登全球最賺錢企業","createTime":"2020-09-09T10:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T02:27:52.000Z","uid":39911,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e2a3ce59e1f26c54236bc1e47a5c1e67483068","tid":2195695,"uid":39911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:42:54.000Z","msg":"根據FactSet Research的統計，股神巴菲特（Warren Buffett）的旗艦投資公司巴郡（Berkshire Hathaway），為第二季度全球最賺錢企業，而在本港上市的工商銀行（1398）及阿里巴巴（9988），分別位列第5及第9位。<br />\n<br />\n有關統計是按全球約4.4萬家上市企業以美元計算的淨利潤，排列出全球最賺錢的100家企業，由於各公司的財年起止日期不同，統計是根據3至5月、4至6月或5至7月的季度財報。<br />\n<br />\n第2季全球最賺錢前10大企業分別為：<br />\n1.巴郡：約263.95億美元，主因是其持有的蘋果公司等股票自4月起大升，帶動賬面收益增加<br />\n2.軟銀集團：116.07億美元，主要因為通過出售所持股票等推高利潤<br />\n3.蘋果：112.53億美元<br />\n4.微軟：112.02億美元<br />\n5.工商銀行：90.7億美元<br />\n6.Google母公司Alphabet：69.59億美元<br />\n7.中國銀行：68.18億美元<br />\n8.沙特阿美：67.55億美元<br />\n9.阿里巴巴：67.13億美元<br />\n10.銀瑞達：66.51億美元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.marketdigest.io/article/市場熱話/4909/Berkshire\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.marketdigest.io%2Farticle%2F%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%2F4909%2FBerkshire&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg%2Fuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=64296fc7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.marketdigest.io/article/市場熱話/4909/Berkshire</a>"},{"pid":"32fb594eb8222c3012de5881c25fe4a92ccdfec0","tid":2195695,"uid":8439,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"計賬面數無咩意思"},{"pid":"ae7a04dbcca390af25dfe9bdedeb81de4322722f","tid":2195695,"uid":188176,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"32fb594eb8222c3012de5881c25fe4a92ccdfec0","tid":2195695,"uid":8439,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:49:13.000Z","msg":"計賬面數無咩意思"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T10:54:56.000Z","msg":"連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"108cfd11ce51c5175c55a1660e31321